{{Infobox person | name = Erland Dryselius | image = Erland Dryseli (6310965011).jpg | birth_date = 1641 | birth_place = | death_date = 24 April 1708 | death_place = }} '''Erland''' (Benedikt, Brodderi) '''Dryselius''' (1641 – 24 April 1708) was a [[Sweden|Swedish]] [[Lutheran]] [[Minister (Christianity)|minister]], [[historian]], and [[translator]].
